author: battibass
body: The muon HLT DQM modules from DQMOffline/Trigger and HLTriggerOffline/Muon were migrated to DQMEDAlayzer and DQMEDHarvester interface according to: https://twiki.cern.ch/twiki/bin/view/CMS/ThreadedDQM
title: Muon HLT DQM modules migrated to DQMEDAlayzer and DQMEDHarvester interface.
